@system wrote:

If Your Brother Logged In On The Same Computer.

  1. Your Account Has Been Banned.
  2. You Have An ‘Illegal’ Item. (Something That Lags The Server) Sometimes You Get Them Without Realising, Like If The Server Hasnt Been Made For ‘camo’ To Work, Then It Lags When Someone Trys Using.
